  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Synopsis</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Hoi-chan,\" a girl with a yellow hat who kept seeking her parents' love into adulthood.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world of patched-together memories, she continues walking in search of the mother ocean...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How to Play</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players can collect 13 hidden hearts scattered throughout various locations to open the door at the starting point and view the ending.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the strange characters and the music composed specifically for this game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*The setting of this story is original and has no connection to any specific incidents, individuals, religions, or organizations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Details</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endings: 1 type</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Estimated play time: 1 hour</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controls (Keyboard/Gamepad)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Movement: WASD / Left Stick</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Examine: E / X Button</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump/Grab ledge: Space / A Button</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Descend from ledge: E / B Button</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Camera control: Mouse / Right Stick</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use item: E / R Shoulder</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save function: Available</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Streaming Guidelines</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Regarding streaming and let's play videos</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No prior contact is necessary for streaming or creating/posting gameplay videos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are free to create content regardless of monetization.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Precautions</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please refrain from defaming or making aggressive comments toward others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please be respectful toward the game content and other players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special Note</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Niji Voice\" is used for character voices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Synopsis</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Hoi-chan,\" a girl with a yellow hat who kept seeking her parents' love into adulthood.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world of patched-together memories, she continues walking in search of the mother ocean...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How to Play</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players can collect 13 hidden hearts scattered throughout various locations to open the door at the starting point and view the ending.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the strange characters and the music composed specifically for this game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*The setting of this story is original and has no connection to any specific incidents, individuals, religions, or organizations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Details</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endings: 1 type</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Estimated play time: 1 hour</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controls (Keyboard/Gamepad)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Movement: WASD / Left Stick</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Examine: E / X Button</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump/Grab ledge: Space / A Button</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Descend from ledge: E / B Button</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Camera control: Mouse / Right Stick</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use item: E / R Shoulder</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save function: Available</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Streaming Guidelines</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Regarding streaming and let's play videos</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No prior contact is necessary for streaming or creating/posting gameplay videos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are free to create content regardless of monetization.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Precautions</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please refrain from defaming or making aggressive comments toward others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please be respectful toward the game content and other players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special Note</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Niji Voice\" is used for character voices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
